        cohabiting partner/spouse
      </textblock>
    </study_pop>
    <sampling_method>Probability Sample</sampling_method>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  For patients: being a female patient diagnosed with primary breast cancer within the
             last four months

          -  For patients: cohabiting with a male partner/spouse

          -  For partners: being the male cohabiting partner/spouse of a patient diagnosed with
             primary breast cancer within the last four months

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  For patients: previous diagnosis of breast cancer or breast cancer relapse
      </textblock>
